adder_mpi-true-termination.c: A manager-worker pattern program adds up all elements in an array.

diffusion1d_mpi-true-termination.c: An MPI version of diffusion1d solver

diffusion2d_mpi-true-termination.c: An MPI version of diffusion2d solver

